    {
      "name": "Embers Unspent",
      "description": "After the current active character inside a Blazing Threshold or Scorching Threshold triggers a Pyro-related reaction, the Traveler will regain 5 Energy. This can occur once every 12s. Additionally, when a nearby party member triggers a Nightsoul Burst, the Traveler will regain 4 Energy.",
      "icon": "https://gi.yatta.moe/assets/UI/UI_Talent_S_PlayerFire_06.png"
    },
    {
      "name": "Foreign Starfire",
      "description": "Draw new strength from journeys past. For every element you have resonated with, you gain additional buffs.\n\nAdditionally, when nearby party members trigger Nightsoul Burst, Traveler will receive 1 stack of Blade of the Sacred Flame, max 2 stacks. After obtaining 2 stacks of Blade of the Sacred Flame, performing a Charged Attack will consume all stacks of Blade of the Sacred Flame and transform into a special Charged Attack: Inferno.\n\nCharged Attack: Inferno\n· Each Charged Attack hit deals increased, Nightsoul-aligned Pyro DMG. Increase in DMG is equal to 200% of Traveler's ATK.\n· Charged Attack: Inferno can be triggered up to once every 15s.",
      "icon": "https://gi.yatta.moe/assets/UI/UI_Talent_S_PlayerFire_07.png"
    }
  ],
  "constellations": [
    {
      "name": "Starfire's Flowing Light",
